Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.81,0:02:58.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.94,0:03:01.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Là gì vậy? Không, mình đã từng nghe rồi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.94,0:03:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.40,0:03:05.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hình như Fujiwara-san có dùng...
