Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.16,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Twitter... Twitter...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.95,0:03:10.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Thôi, tôi đi tắm đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.49,0:03:15.00,Typeset,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,277)\bord0}Đang sử dụng
